title: JetBrains WebStorm 6.0.2a - for Mac OS X - Inc. Keygen
description:
JetBrains WebStorm 6.0.2a Inc. Keygen for Mac OS X
--------------------------------------------------
This package has been provided to you by DNA.
The keygen has been created by Team EMBRACE.


 Installation instructions:
============================
  1. Run the 'WebStorm-6.0.2a.dmg'
  2. Move the 'WebStorm.app' icon to Applications folder
  3. Open Terminal
  4. Navigate (cd) to Keygen location
  5. Extract the ta.gz file by running "tar -xzf keygen.tar.gz", and then execute "./keygen"
  6. Enter your username, and press enter
  7. Copy the key (including the = [equal] signs), with Cmd+C
  8. Open WebStorm from your application folder
  9. On the license screen enter your username and the license code you've copied on step 7
 10. Enjoy!

 Note:
=======
 If the keygen execution fails, you'll probably need to install developer tools.
 Search on google "How do I install Apple Developer Tools on my Mac".
